  "prompt": "What is the best digital marketing course in Kolkata?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" digital marketing course in Kolkata depends on your specific needs, budget, and learning goals. However, here are some highly regarded options based on reputation, course content, and student reviews:\n\n---\n\n### **Top Digital Marketing Courses in Kolkata**\n1. **Digital Academy 360**  \n   - **Why Choose?**  \n     Offers a comprehensive curriculum with hands-on training, certifications, and placement assistance.  \n   - **Key Features:**  \n     - Live online and offline classes  \n     - Covers SEO, SEM, Social Media Marketing, Content Marketing, and more  \n     - Industry-relevant projects and internships  \n   - **Location:** Multiple centers in Kolkata  \n\n2. **NIIT (Digital Marketing Course)**  \n   - **Why Choose?**  \n     Known for its structured curriculum and brand reputation.  \n   - **Key Features:**  \n     - Advanced modules in analytics, PPC, and email marketing  \n     - Placement support  \n     - Flexible learning options  \n   - **Location:** Multiple centers in Kolkata  \n\n3. **IFBI (Institute of Finance, Banking, and Insurance)**  \n   - **Why Choose?**  \n     Offers a blend of digital marketing and analytics training.  \n   - **Key Features:**  \n     - Focus on practical applications  \n     - Industry-relevant workshops and case studies  \n   - **Location:** Kolkata  \n\n4. **Arena Animation (Digital Marketing Program)**  \n   - **Why Choose?**  \n     Popular for its creative approach to digital marketing.  \n   - **Key Features:**  \n     - Covers social media, content creation, and video marketing  \n     - Hands-on training with tools and software  \n   - **Location:** Multiple centers in Kolkata  \n\n5. **Kolkata Digital Marketing Academy (KDM)**  \n   - **Why Choose?**  \n     Specializes in affordable and practical digital marketing training.  \n   - **Key Features:**  \n     - Small batch sizes for personalized attention  \n     - Focus on live projects and certifications  \n   - **Location:** Kolkata  \n\n6. **IIM SKILLS (Digital Marketing Course)**  \n   - **Why Choose?**  \n     Offers one of the best online digital marketing courses with practical training.  \n   - **Key Features:**  \n     - Covers all aspects of digital marketing  \n     - Certifications and freelance opportunities  \n   - **Location:** Online (accessible from Kolkata)  \n\n7. **IMS Proschool (Digital Marketing Course)**  \n   - **Why Choose?**  \n     Known for its industry-oriented training.  \n   - **Key Features:**  \n     - Practical training with real-world projects  \n     - Placement support  \n   - **Location:** Kolkata  \n\n---\n\n### **Factors to Consider When Choosing a Course**\n1. **Course Content:** Ensure it covers essential topics like SEO, SEM, social media, analytics, and content marketing.  \n2. **Trainers:** Look for courses with industry-experts as trainers.  \n3. **Certifications:** Check if the course provides globally recognized certifications.  \n4. **Placement Support:** If you\u2019re looking for a job, opt for courses with placement assistance.  \n5. **Reviews and Testimonials:** Research student feedback and success stories.  \n6. **Budget:** Compare fees and ensure the course offers good value for money.  \n\n---\n\n### **Recommendation**\nIf you\u2019re looking for comprehensive training with placement support, **Digital Academy 360** and **NIIT** are excellent choices. For an affordable and practical option, consider **Kolkata Digital Marketing Academy (KDM)** or **Arena Animation**. For online flexibility, **IIM SKILLS** is a great pick.  \n\nAlways visit the institute or attend a demo session to make an informed decision!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
